@node "Introd" " MV Comment - Introduction"
@next "disclaim"
@prev "main"

Yes, you are right, there are already many Comment doors for DayDream, but...

I thought that it would not be bad to write another one Comment door...
This is first release, and only main features are included... but,
soon... it will be much better and some nice options will be added.

If you have any idea for Comment door, contact @{"author" Link Author}.


@endnode

