 I hope that users will need no manuals to use door ? O:)

@endnode


@node Registration " MV Comment - Registration"
@next "Author"
@prev "user"

        @{fg shine}@{u} REGISTRATION @{uu}@{fg text}

 MV Comment Door is EMailware, that means if you like (or not) door,
 you are supposed to send EMAIL to @{"author" Link author}.

 If you find any bug or have some idea for improving MV Comment Door, 
 feel free to contact @{"author" Link author}.

 Door is no crippled in any way.

 Look at @{"other Mad Virgin products" Link MVProd}.



@endnode

